      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<h3 id=\"StylizedCanvas-CanvasisaDisplayFiltertofacilitatelayeringoftextures,color,oranyotherexistinglayerintherenderbetweenotherStylizedLookslayers(Lines,Toon,Hatching).ResultDisableCanvasFinalLayerSeeexampledemovideohttps://vimeo.com/921627751:https://vimeo.com/\"><div class=\"conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-macro-name=\"include\" data-macro-id=\"ed0a2927-ab6f-4b9f-ab59-af05d22eacfa\"><p>Canvas is a Display Filter to facilitate layering of textures, color, or any other existing layer in the render between other Stylized Looks layers (Lines, Toon, Hatching).</p><h4 id=\"StylizedCanvas-Result\">Result</h4><ul><li><p>Disable</p></li><li><p>Canvas Final</p></li></ul><h4 id=\"StylizedCanvas-Layer\">Layer</h4><p>See&nbsp;<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://vimeo.com/921627751\" rel=\"nofollow\">example demo video</a>:<br/></p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://vimeo.com/921627751\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542235305/canvas.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330764264&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542235305/canvas.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330764264&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"340\" data-width=\"614\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542235324\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"canvas.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542235305\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"3cbcf90d-6531-48a1-8deb-0a88c78748e8\" data-media-type=\"file\"/></span></a><h4 id=\"StylizedCanvas-CanvasAOV\">Canvas AOV</h4><p>Name of a color AOV to use for this Layer. This AOV has to be setup in Maya/Katana/Houdini or this Canvas DisplayFilter will exit.</p><p>See&nbsp;<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.vimeo.com/921628311\" rel=\"nofollow\">example demo video</a> with Canvas + Hatching:</p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.vimeo.com/921628311\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542235305/canvas2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330764263&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542235305/canvas2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330764263&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"344\" data-width=\"614\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542235321\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"canvas2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542235305\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d73238d4-ca46-4841-b081-db9311cf3085\" data-media-type=\"file\"/></span></a><h4 id=\"StylizedCanvas-CanvasColor\">Canvas Color</h4><p>Background color outside of alpha.</p><h4 id=\"StylizedCanvas-CanvasTexture\">Canvas Texture</h4><p>Provide BG texture for outside alpha, if blank uses BG Color</p><h4 id=\"StylizedCanvas-IgnoreAlpha\">Ignore Alpha</h4><p>Put BG Color or Texture on everything under Canvas, ignoring alpha.</p><h2 id=\"StylizedCanvas-CompositingPage\">Compositing Page</h2><h4 id=\"StylizedCanvas-CompMode\">Comp Mode</h4><p>Comp on Color or previous layer (BG)<br/><strong>Over</strong><br/><strong>Multiply</strong><br/><strong>Screen&nbsp;</strong></p><h4 id=\"StylizedCanvas-Gamma\">Gamma</h4><h4 id=\"StylizedCanvas-Mix\">Mix</h4><p>0: disables this Canvas Node and shows previous node if daisy chained, or original beauty if no previous Stylized Looks nodes. <br/>1: full Canvas from this node.</p></div></h3><p><br/></p>"
    }
